00:00:43.600 --> 00:00:47.039
 And so we don't actually have, we have a lot of middles of books,

00:00:47.039 --> 00:00:52.440
 but we don't have a lot of, if it's a single book, the beginning and end are always the most vulnerable.

00:00:52.440 --> 00:00:56.920
 P66 preserves for us the beginning of the Gospel of John.

